16:35.627 --> 16:37.795
Hey.

16:37.796 --> 16:39.329
What are you doing up,
little man?

16:39.330 --> 16:41.799
It's 3:00
in the morning.

16:41.800 --> 16:43.100
Can't sleep?

16:43.101 --> 16:45.469
What's the matter?

16:45.470 --> 16:48.338
Dad, are you gonna die?

16:48.339 --> 16:52.576
Not till I've
paid for these knives.

16:52.577 --> 16:54.812
Come over here.
What's the matter with you?

16:54.813 --> 16:57.414
You told wilson
you're going to die.

16:57.415 --> 16:58.482
You heard that?

16:58.483 --> 17:00.618
I was in the tree.

17:00.619 --> 17:03.353
Well, I didn't mean
I was gonna die now.

17:03.354 --> 17:05.089
I'm gonna live
for a long, long time.

17:05.089 --> 17:07.758
But your dad died
when you were a kid.

17:09.460 --> 17:12.630
That doesn't mean anything's
gonna happen to me.

17:12.631 --> 17:15.464
But what if it does?

17:17.234 --> 17:20.137
Well, I'll find
somebody really cool
to take care of you.

17:20.137 --> 17:21.905
Like al?

17:27.545 --> 17:29.312
He'll assist that person.

17:31.082 --> 17:34.952
If you're not gonna die,
why do you need a will?

17:34.953 --> 17:36.153
'cause, uh...

17:36.154 --> 17:39.256
Honey? That's just something

17:39.257 --> 17:43.027
That every responsible adult
has to do.

17:43.028 --> 17:45.462
That's what I was gonna say.

17:45.463 --> 17:47.164
You don't have to worry
about that stuff.

17:47.165 --> 17:51.601
No, you only have to
worry about vegetables

17:51.602 --> 17:54.638
And cleaning up
your own room

17:54.639 --> 17:56.840
And making sure
your brothers

17:56.841 --> 18:00.844
Don't rocket you
over the house.

18:00.845 --> 18:02.612
Besides, you don't have
to worry about that.

18:02.613 --> 18:04.782
Just know that
your mom and I...
Shh.

18:17.729 --> 18:21.098
