while you're still alive.

21:53.444 --> 21:54.945
He gave everything to you?

21:54.946 --> 21:59.016
Yep, just like you.

21:59.017 --> 22:01.851
You know, honey,
I've been thinking.

22:01.852 --> 22:05.622
If I die first,
I want you to remarry.

22:05.623 --> 22:07.457
