would it be?

22:26.677 --> 22:31.681
Well, I guess
I'd look for a woman
that was alive.

22:31.682 --> 22:34.818
That would make it easier
to get the blood test.

22:34.819 --> 22:36.353
Maybe I'd...

22:36.354 --> 22:39.056
Well, I'd want someone
who's a good mom,

22:39.057 --> 22:42.092
Sensitive and caring,

22:42.093 --> 22:44.627
Good sense of humor,
